itzerland|type=album|award=Gold|title=Lemonade|artist=Beyonc\u00e9|relyear=2016|certyear=2017|accessdate=November 30, 2016}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|type=album|region=United Kingdom|artist=Beyonc\u00e9|title=Lemonade|award=Platinum|salesamount=387,000|salesref=<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/beyonces-number-1-album-lemonade-will-finally-get-a-wider-streaming-release-on-april-23__26110/|title=Beyonce's Number 1 album Lemonade will finally get a wider streaming release on April 23|last=Myers|first=Justin|date=April 18, 2019|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=April 19, 2019}}</ref>|relyear=2016|certyear=2016}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|type=album|region=United States|artist=Beyonc\u00e9|title=Lemonade|award=Platinum|number=3|certyear=2019|date=June 12, 2019|accessdate=July 8, 2019|salesamount=1,554,000<!--this is Pure sales per Nielsen SoundScan source, don't change it-->|salesref=<ref name=\"billboard\"/>}}\n{{Certification Table Summary}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Worldwide|nocert=true|salesamount=2,500,000|salesref=<ref name=\"WW sales\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2017.pdf|title=Global Music Report 2017|publisher=[[IFPI]] |date=April 25, 2017 |accessdate=July 8, 2019 }}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of release dates, showing region, format(s), label(s) and reference(s).\n! scope=\"col\" | Region\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Format(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Label(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | Various<!--Impossible to source release to the entire populated land mass of the planet.-->\n| {{Start date|mf=yes|2016|04|23}}\n| [[Streaming media|Streaming]] {{small|([[Tidal (service)|Tidal]] exclusive)}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| {{Flatlist |\n* [[Parkwood Entertainment|Parkwood]]\n* [[Columbia Records|Columbia]]\n}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref